This software was developed as part of research on chemotherapy resistance
dynamics in ovarian cancer.

Data used with this software is sourced from:
  Hockings et al. (2025). Subclonal copy-number alterations drive resistance
  to platinum-based chemotherapy in ovarian cancer.
  Cancer Research. DOI: 10.1158/0008-5472.CAN-25-0351

  Mendeley Dataset: DOI 10.17632/m93sk9n767.1

